TemplateBody:
AWSTemplateFormatVersion: '2010-09-09'
Resources:
  Role:
    Type: AWS::IAM::Role
    Properties:
      RoleName: 'cloudrail-viewonly-arorghqdxpdu-role'
      ManagedPolicyArns:
      - arn:aws:iam::aws:policy/SecurityAudit
      - arn:aws:iam::aws:policy/job-function/ViewOnlyAccess
      AssumeRolePolicyDocument:
        Version: '2012-10-17'
        Statement:
        - Effect: Allow
          Principal:
            AWS: 645376637575
          Action: sts:AssumeRole
          Condition:
            StringEquals:
              sts:ExternalId: 'aiotahfiumog'

Outputs:
  RoleName:
    Description: Your role name
    Value:
      Ref: Role
